      • setConsumptionValue

        public void setConsumptionValue(int value,
                                com.freedomotic.model.ds.Config params,
                                boolean fireCommand)
        Update the power consumption value. This behavior is supposed to be read only by design, so no commands are executed even if the fireCommand property is set to true.
        Parameters:
        value - the new consumption value
        params - general request parameters
        fireCommand - true if a command should executed by the related plugin, false if this is just a thing status update
